name: SONG FOR @808unexpected
description:
-SOUND ON-

@808unexpected is a musician and 3D artist with a focus on the immersive experience. In each of his works, the spectator is absorbed by the audiovisual proposal. Almost like being suspended in a kind of meditation. In addition to being an incredible artist he is a friend, one of the first I met in this landscape and who has been very supportive with me. He is truly an unbelievable person. For this special song he said to me to do whatever I want, to put my mind in blank and create. And that it´s what I did, I wanted to explore some different kind of musical places. Here's what I brought back from that exploratory trip… 

Dibaxu // tw: @dibaxuP

*This is a collection of special and dedicated song for those collectors that get #1, #2, #3 and #4 for my “Annotations” collection. If you get it, let me know and I will do something special for you, this is a lifetime offer.
